The Soul Sisters: Conversation 07
"Nostalgia & the Tech-Free Childhood"
Rewind to the days of landline phones, outdoor games, Doordarshan evenings, and handwritten letters.

Before screens ruled our world we had a life full of connection, chaos, and charm.
Catch us as we dive into the magic of growing up in the 80s & 90s, when childhood meant more sky and less scroll.

Now live on YouTube ☕🧡 Saree Sponsor @katha.forwomen

latestPosts.caption:
🎙️ The Soul Sisters Present: A Retro Conversation! 🎞️💾💿

To all the 90s memories of a VCR tape of old movies, and rewinding with a pencil wasn’t just for cassettes but for life?

We’re talking:
📼 Video cassettes & Doordarshan 
💽 Floppy disks and snake games
💿 CDs that played your favourite indie pop hits
🎮 Brick games, Mario, and Contra before WiFi was a thing
📞 One landline, zero privacy and we still survived!

We're rewinding the reel for a conversation full of feels, laughter, and memories only a true 90s teen will get. 🥹💛

Stay tuned!
📺 Coming soon on The Soul Sisters YouTube Channel
Because growing up once wasn’t enough ! we’re reliving it 💃🕺

#TheSoulSisters #90sNostalgia #RetroReel #IndianTeen90s #VCRToCD #OldSchoolCool #DesiThrowback #ChildhoodRewind #ComingSoon

🎞️✨ The Soul Sisters Conversation Presents: A Trip Down 90s Memory Lane! 🇮🇳📼

🎮 Remember blowing into video game cartridges to make them work?
📺 The joy of renting video cassettes for weekend family movies…
📱 Your cool cousin flashing the first Motorola mobile phone?
🍬 A fistful of colorful Gems and the slow joy of unwrapping Ravalgaon toffees…

💬 Nostalgia is calling. And we’re answering.
Join us for a heartwarming conversation on the golden 90s era in India—
from the taste of childhood to the tech of the times.

🧡 Coming soon on YouTube

Special post for my Mama - to the strongest, kindest, goofiest, most amazing woman I know.

Your love, strength, confidence, and care have shaped me into who I am. From your delicious food to your magical home remedies, from your resilience in tough times to your constant positivity — you’ve been my healer, and my inspiration.

I love you for everything you are and everything you’ve made me. ❤️
